The implement of CINFE on AD bulk data is shown as examples in this project. The input data can be changed with the other datasets if necessary.

Calculating causal total network flow entropy (CTNFE) input data: express_matrix.csv, network.txt; output data: CTNFE_all_samples.csv running pipeline: calculate CTNFE.py

Calculating causal external network flow entropy (CENFE) input data: express_matrix.csv, network.txt; output data: CENFE_all_samples.csv running pipeline: calculate CENFE.py

Calculating causal internal network flow entropy (CINFE) and displaying result running pipeline input data: CTNFE_all_samples.csv, CENFE_all_samples.csv; running pipeline: CINFE.m 
